  "1764280": {
    "name": "Dungeons of the Amber Griffin",
    "steam_appid": 1764280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/3820fcc0b213e38b1e75bac9a05b7335.avif?t=1759131212\" width=610 height=172 /></span><br><br>准备好踏上神秘卡舒比亚的激动人心的旅程。了解古代波美拉尼亚人的信仰，并与开始在周围泛滥的怪物作斗争。通过打败怪物，收集信息，填充基于卡舒比亚故事的怪物图鉴。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪物图鉴</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/b83197a0781a49479228af8476c28c4e.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/b83197a0781a49479228af8476c28c4e.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/b83197a0781a49479228af8476c28c4e.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我们与韦赫罗沃的卡舒比亚-波美拉尼亚文学和音乐博物馆合作，创建了一个独特的、在cRPG游戏中前所未有的卡舒比亚幻想世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的角色职业</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/c0b832baa9220920e5bb8084140e964b.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/c0b832baa9220920e5bb8084140e964b.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/c0b832baa9220920e5bb8084140e964b.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>组建一个由4个具有不同技能的勇敢冒险者组成的团队，这些技能将在战斗中派上用场。选择例如WÒJÔRZ（战士）、DULAS（盗贼）、ŻÉRCA（祭司）、KÙTIN（法师）等职业，并决定他们的发展方向。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能系统</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/f606672c0f8305d6a319f13e95dd86a8.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/f606672c0f8305d6a319f13e95dd86a8.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/f606672c0f8305d6a319f13e95dd86a8.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在你的团队升级过程中，你将决定其发展的方向，这将对战斗机制产生决定性的影响。被动技能将帮助你在艰难的战斗中生存或增强基础技能，例如允许携带更多的物品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏中的物品</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/1ae958be7545f61df8ba6932c8d24736.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/1ae958be7545f61df8ba6932c8d24736.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/1ae958be7545f61df8ba6932c8d24736.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收集你团队的装备，这将帮助你在黑暗的幻想世界中生存。游戏世界中有武器、盔甲、神器、魔法卷轴、黄金和必需的补给。在旅途中，你将发现许多在卡舒比亚独特的物品，例如治疗植物、有毒蘑菇和所谓的卡舒比亚符文系统Merki。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/cd9f43f32aeea63a10587fbf4258c353.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/cd9f43f32aeea63a10587fbf4258c353.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/cd9f43f32aeea63a10587fbf4258c353.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在游戏中获得经验时，你将解锁魔法书中的新咒语。你可以使用战斗咒语来帮助你对抗怪物和恶魔。被动咒语将保护你的团队并增强魔法物品的效果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界地图</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/605cff8ae6c5b45cdec48063fd711c62.poster.avif?t=1759131212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/605cff8ae6c5b45cdec48063fd711c62.webm?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/605cff8ae6c5b45cdec48063fd711c62.mp4?t=1759131212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我们根据真实的地理位置创建神奇的卡舒比亚世界。地名来自卡舒比亚语，这是一种濒危语言，但仍由生活在波兰北部地区的社区使用。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >非玩家角色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/1c48ce9ac2e5fd55372d17d7651a0bc6.avif?t=1759131212\" width=610 height=444 /></span><br>在神奇的卡舒比亚世界中，你会遇到许多有趣的人物，你可以与他们交谈、交易并完成大大小小的任务。居民的故事深受卡舒比亚人真实信仰和迷信的影响。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实的传说</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764280/extras/f5351d27384fdca22ce3aa09f200bb51.avif?t=1759131212\" width=610 height=358 /></span><br>游戏的主要情节与狮鹫的形象有关，根据卡舒比亚的一个传说，狮鹫在卡舒比亚的某个未知地点隐藏了一大块琥珀。直到20世纪初，卡舒比亚仍有挖出死者尸体并用特制的铲子砍掉头颅的案例。人们相信这些是所谓的wieszczi或òpi，他们死后从坟墓中爬起来，杀死自己的家人。",
